      <body>
         <pb n="1" facs="../images/ew_b5_1580_001.jpg"/>
         <head>
            <hi rend="right">
               <name type="place" subtype="address">
               <choice><abbr>Fla.</abbr><expan>Florida</expan></choice>
               State <choice><abbr>Hospt.</abbr><expan>Hospital</expan></choice><lb/><location><geo>30.706597 -84.841442</geo></location></name><lb/>
               <name type="place" subtype="city">Chattahoochee, <choice><abbr>Fla</abbr><expan>Florida</expan></choice></name><lb/>
               <date when="1929-04-10"><choice><abbr>4 - 10 - 29</abbr><expan>April tenth, nineteen twenty-nine</expan></choice></date><lb/>
            </hi>
         </head>
            <opener>
               <salute>
                  Dear <name type="person">Miss White</name> :<lb/>
               </salute>
            </opener>
         <p>
            <hi rend="right">Only a few lines</hi><lb/>
            to let you hear from me. This<lb/>
            leaves me well hoping that this<lb/>
            will find you well.<lb/>
           </p>
         <p>
            <hi rend="right"><name type="person">Miss White</name> I am very</hi><lb/>
            anxious to get back home. And<lb/>
            if you will get in touch with the<lb/>
            <choice><sic>Superintendant</sic><corr>Superintendent</corr></choice> and see about<lb/>
            getting me out I will pay you<lb/>
            <choice><orig>what ever</orig><reg>whatever</reg></choice> the cost is when I get<lb/>
            home. And I do wish that you see<lb/>
            about my things and take charge<lb/>
            of them until I get back.<lb/>
         </p>
         <p rend="indent">
            This is the <choice><abbr>Supt.</abbr><expan>Superintendent</expan></choice> address.<lb/>
            <name type="person"><choice><abbr>Dr.</abbr><expan>Doctor</expan></choice> J. Q. Folmar</name>, <name type="place" subtype="address"><choice><abbr>Fla.</abbr><expan>Florida</expan></choice> State <choice><abbr>Hospt.</abbr><expan>Hospital</expan></choice><lb/><location><geo>30.706597 -84.841442</geo></location></name>
         </p>
         <p>
            you must not believe anything<lb/>
            wrong of me for I am the same as when<lb/>
            you first<choice><orig>.</orig><reg/></choice> <supplied reason="omitted-in-original">met</supplied> me<choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice> Tell my pastor &amp; Deacon to do all they<lb/>
            can for me.
         </p>
         <closer>
            <salute>
               <hi rend="center">your sister in Christ.</hi><lb/>
            </salute>
                  <signed>
                     <hi rend="right"><name type="person">Sarah Best</name>.</hi><lb/>
                  </signed>
               </closer>
      </body>
